The Writers' Room - Season 2 - Episode 2 (WEB-DL - MP4)
-------------------------------------------------------

The Writers' Room, hosted by Academy Award winning writer, Jim Rash,
gets real with the most innovative voices in TV today. This season,
visit the writers and creative teams behind Scandal, House of Cards,
The Good Wife, Sons of Anarchy, Pretty Little Liars and The Walking Dead,
Superman and other Comic Book Adaptations. With shocking revelations and
hilariously candid comments, The Writers' Room provides a never-before-seen
window into what makes great TV.

Produced by Relativity Television and Sundance Channel.


Host Jim Rash explores the world of comic book adaptations for TV
with 'The Walking Dead' Creator Robert Kirkman and 'Smallville'
Creators Al Gough and Miles Millar. Pop culture expert Blair Butler
and TV Guide's Michael Schneider join the chat.
